    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Material comprising the leaves and pithy or hollow stems of grasslike plants of the genus Juncus, found in wet or marshy places and used since ancient times to make baskets, mats, and chair seats.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
